text: The women's doubles tennis event of the 2011 Pan American Games was held on October 18–21 at the Telcel Tennis Complex in Guadalajara.Tennis technical manual The defending Pan American Games champions were Jorgelina Cravero and Betina Jozami of Argentina. ==Seeds== ==Draw== Women's doubles draw ===Finals=== ===Top half=== ===Bottom half=== ==References== Category:Tennis at the 2011 Pan American Games
